Title: Toolkit for Data Cleaning in Psychology
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jason Moy
Maintainer: Jason Moy <jasonmoy28@gmail.com>
Description: The package contains several useful functions for data cleaning for psychological research, such as compositing scores, recoding items, and summarizing number of NA values in a dataframe. 
